      <title>美国和东南亚的亿万富翁称高税收是最大风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/billionaire-family-offices-in-us-southeast-asia-say-higher-taxes-are-top-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份新报告显示，美国和东南亚的亿万富翁家庭表示，高税收是未来五年最大的风险，超过了重大冲突和气候变化等其他担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/billionaire-family-offices-in-us-southeast-asia-say-higher-taxes-are-top-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯制定了与北约竞争对手转移波罗的海边界的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/russia-sets-out-plan-to-shift-baltic-sea-border-with-nato-rivals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯国防部制定了改变该国波罗的海边界并扩大其毗邻北约竞争对手的领海的计划，引起了立陶宛和芬兰的强烈反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/russia-sets-out-plan-to-shift-baltic-sea-border-with-nato-rivals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 07:07:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英镑上涨，英国通胀后交易商削减降息押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/pound-rallies-traders-pare-bets-on-rate-cuts-after-uk-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示四月份通胀放缓程度低于预期后，英镑升至两个月来的最高水平，交易员预计降息幅度将减少且放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/pound-rallies-traders-pare-bets-on-rate-cuts-after-uk-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 06:42:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
